<%# app/views/vendor/contracts/show.html.erb - Step 13: Contract Display %>
<% content_for :title, "Contrato - Movicuotas" %>

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#125282]">Contrato de Crédito</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Revise los términos y condiciones del contrato antes de proceder a la firma digital.</p>

    <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium text-blue-800">Cliente: <%= @contract.loan.customer.full_name %></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-600">Contrato: <%= @contract.loan.contract_number %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contract Display -->
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden mb-8 border border-gray-200">
    <!-- Contract Header Bar -->
    <div class="bg-[#125282] text-white p-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">CONTRATO MOVICUOTAS</h2>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Documento legal - Paso 13 de 18</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-right">
        <p class="text-sm">Válido hasta: <%= I18n.l(Date.today + 30.days, format: :long) %></p>
        <p class="text-xs opacity-80">Generado el <%= I18n.l(Date.today, format: :long) %></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contract Content -->
    <div class="p-0">
      <%= raw @contract_html %>
    </div>

    <!-- Action Buttons -->
    <div class="p-6 border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            <span class="font-medium">Estado:</span>
            <% if @contract.signed? %>
              <span class="ml-2 px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Firmado</span>
            <% else %>
              <span class="ml-2 px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Pendiente de firma</span>
            <% end %>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <%= link_to "← Volver", vendor_customer_search_path, class: "px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" %>

          <% if @contract.signed? %>
            <%= link_to "Continuar →", "#", class: "px-6 py-3 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors font-medium" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Aceptar y Proceder a Firma →", signature_vendor_contract_path(@contract), class: "px-6 py-3 bg-[#125282] text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-[#0f4670] transition-colors font-medium" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Important Notes -->
  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-800 text-lg mb-3 flex items-center">
      <svg class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.998-.833-2.732 0L4.342 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"/>
      </svg>
      Notas Importantes
    </h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-amber-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Este contrato es un documento legal vinculante. Asegúrese de entender todos los términos antes de firmar.</li>
      <li>La firma digital tiene la misma validez legal que una firma física.</li>
      <li>Una vez firmado, el contrato se almacenará digitalmente y podrá descargarse en cualquier momento.</li>
      <li>El cliente recibirá una copia del contrato firmado en su correo electrónico (si fue proporcionado).</li>
      <li>Para cualquier duda, contacte al departamento legal de MOVICUOTAS.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Progress Indicator -->
  <div class="mt-12">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#125282] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold">13</div>
        <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700">Contrato</span>
      </div>
      <div class="h-1 flex-1 mx-4 bg-gray-200">
        <div class="h-1 bg-[#125282] w-1/2"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-300 text-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">14</div>
        <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-500">Firma Digital</span>
      </div>
      <div class="h-1 flex-1 mx-4 bg-gray-200"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-300 text-gray-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">15</div>
        <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-500">Crédito Aplicado</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Paso 13 de 18 - Flujo de Venta</p>
  </div>
</div>